  LocalName:
  - Whoa!/Who are You?
  - My name's Daring Do. Do You need a help?/If You lost, I have a camp.../Near from the temple.../I'll just show it on the map.
  - Yes... I mean.../Thank You for saving/of The Great and Powerful Trixie!
  - See You later.../In Your camp.
